    play cost by 5.\n[On Play] [When Digivolving] Suspend all of your opponent's
    Digimon and 1 of your Digimon gets +3000 DP for the turn. Then, 1 of your Digimon
    may attack.\n[End of Your Turn] This Digimon and any of your other Digimon may
    DNA digivolve into a Digimon card with [Chaosmon]\_in its name in the hand. Then,
    the DNA digivolved Digimon may attack."
